  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK186">
<l>piṟaṉpaḻi kūṟuvāṉ ṟaṉpaḻi yuḷḷun</l>
<l>tiṟaṉṟerintu kūṟap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The character of the faults of that man who publishes abroad the faults of others will be sought out and published.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
